          ],
          "answer": "$|z| = 2\\sqrt{2}$, $\\arg z = -\\dfrac{\\pi}{4}$",
          "solution": "$$|z| = \\sqrt{2^2 + (-2)^2} = \\sqrt{8} = 2\\sqrt{2},\\qquad \\arg z = -\\frac{\\pi}{4}.$$",
          "verify": [
            "Eq(Abs(2 - 2*I), 2*sqrt(2))",
            "Eq(arg(2 - 2*I), -pi/4)"
