              "note": "$z = 2\\sqrt{2}\\,\\operatorname{cis}\\!\\left(-\\dfrac{\\pi}{4}\\right)$"
            }
          ],
          "answer": "$z = 2\\sqrt{2}\\,\\operatorname{cis}\\!\\left(-\\dfrac{\\pi}{4}\\right)$",
          "solution": "$$z = 2\\sqrt{2}\\left(\\cos\\!\\left(-\\tfrac{\\pi}{4}\\right) + i\\sin\\!\\left(-\\tfrac{\\pi}{4}\\right)\\right).$$",
          "verify": [
