          "answer": "$\\cos x = \\dfrac{1}{2}$",
          "solution": "$$(2\\cos x - 1)(\\cos x + 2) = 0 \\Rightarrow \\cos x = \\tfrac12 \\text{ or } \\cos x = -2.$$ Since $-1 \\le \\cos x \\le 1$, only $\\cos x = \\tfrac12$ is valid.",
          "verify": [
            "Eq(expand((2*k - 1)*(k + 2)), 2*k**2 + 3*k - 2)",
