          "solution": "$$\\frac{dA}{dr} = 8\\pi r, \\qquad \\frac{dA}{dt} = 8\\pi(5)\\cdot\\frac{1}{\\pi} = 40 \\text{ cm}^2\\text{ s}^{-1}.$$",
