              "note": "$P(X = 2) = \\dfrac{8}{27}$"
            }
          ],
          "answer": "$\\dfrac{8}{27}$",
          "solution": "$$P(X = 2) = \\binom{4}{2}\\left(\\frac13\\right)^2\\left(\\frac23\\right)^2 = 6\\cdot\\frac19\\cdot\\frac49 = \\frac{8}{27}.$$",
          "verify": [
